E4Plus1.uk.description: The Jimmy Jab Games: When the squad have time to kill, Peralta launches the seventh annual Jimmy Jab Games, an eccentric series of contests held in the precinct building. (S2 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Halloween II: Peralta and Holt repeat their Halloween wager, as Peralta bets the Captain that he can steal his watch before midnight. (S2 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Natural Born Kissers: Homer and Marge spice up their love life by snuggling in public places, including a barn and the crazy golf course. But then they lose their clothes... (S9 Ep25/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: My Mother the Carjacker: Homer's long-lost mother (guest star Glenn Close) arranges to meet him. But after she's apprehended by police, Homer must free her from a prison bus. (S15 Ep2/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Crazy Calls: Murray and Pop-Pop get answering machines but then wage a message war on each other. Beverly worries when Adam befriends some computer geeks. (S4 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Stefan King: Adam gets into trouble with Beverly for portraying her as a monster in a horror story, and Erica forces Barry to go to a Halloween costume dance with her. (S4 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Five Minutes: Mitch and Cam have five minutes to catch a flight, and Haley and Rainer are forced to re-evaluate their entire relationship in five minutes. (S8 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Frank's Wedding: Frank Dunphy's Roaring Twenties-themed wedding day is finally here, and to get into the spirit, Phil gets the Dunphy clan to show up in costume. (S8 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Payback: The squad decide that it's high time for Peralta to pay them back all the money they've lent him over the years. Santiago and Holt reopen an arson case. (S2 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Defense Rests: Sophia's job gets in the way of her relationship with Peralta. Deputy Chief Wuntch needs Captain Holt's help with a job recommendation. (S2 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Margical Mystery Tour: The Springfield Library doesn't have enough books to help with the kids' research papers, so Marge steps in with some anecdotes on historical figures. (S15 Ep11/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Milhouse Doesn't Live Here Anymore: Milhouse moves away from town, and Bart comes to realise just how much his pathetic friend means to him. (S15 Ep12/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: A scare leaves Cleo and Sienna in turmoil. Tinhead resorts to drastic measures to hide his scheming. And Mercedes struggles to adjust to a change in her life.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Stealing First Base: When Bart's class is temporarily merged with another at school, he has to share a desk with a girl called Nikki and soon develops a crush on her. (S21 Ep15/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Aaron, who won TV's The Traitors, is out on a date with a straight-A student Laura. Plus: a date on roller skates and a Mr Bean impression. (S21 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: On the 'Box: Bridgerton, Britain's Got Talent, Inside No. 9, My Strange Addiction: Still Addicted?, Top of the Pops 1984 and The War on Britain's Motorists: Dispatches (S23 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: Britain's sharpest armchair critics share their insightful and passionate takes on the best TV shows of early 2024. (S23 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Open House: The Great Sex...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...Experiment: Brave couples move into the Open House. Chloe and Paul, who've only ever had sex with each other, open their relationship up to see if Chloe's attracted to women. (S3 Ep1/8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction
E4Plus1.uk.description: Two more hopeful singletons join Anna Richardson in the Naked Attraction studio, including martial arts instructor Ryan, who was born with cystic fibrosis. (S3 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Aaron, who won TV's The Traitors, is out on a date with a straight-A student Laura. Plus: a date on roller skates and a Mr Bean impression. (S21 Ep5) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: On the 'Box: Bridgerton, Britain's Got Talent, Inside No. 9, My Strange Addiction: Still Addicted?, Top of the Pops 1984 and The War on Britain's Motorists: Dispatches (S23 Ep15) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: Britain's sharpest armchair critics share their insightful and passionate takes on the best TV shows of early 2024. (S23 Ep16) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Mama Drama: Adam is disappointed to be cast in a minor role in the school musical, so Beverly helps him to land a leading part in a competing stage show. (S2 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Facts of Bleeping Life: Barry and Adam put together a garage rock band, and ask Lainey and Erica to get involved - leading to unexpected consequences. (S2 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Don't Tell the Bride
E4Plus1.uk.description: The One on a Caravan Site: Lauren wants to feel unique at her wedding, but her groom plans their nuptials at the same caravan park that Lauren visits every year...

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Ten Years Later: Claire is determined to make up for her less-than-joyful mood at Jay and Gloria's wedding by throwing their 10th-anniversary party. (S9 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Winner Winner Turkey Dinner: Jay's Thanksgiving toast honours the entire family on their recent successes, even though everyone knows that they aren't quite true. (S9 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip from Rude Tube's naughty little sister, Rude(ish) Tube, featuring sports of the lawnmower, motorbike and bicycle variety.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Michon's: Can Gordon help the unwell owner of a family-run Atlanta smokehouse address his daughter's hands-off management style? (S5 Ep11) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Zocalo: Gordon Ramsay visits a floundering Mexican restaurant which has become an albatross around the necks of its owners, married couple Greg and Mary Russell. (S5 Ep12) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Dungeons & Dragons, Anyone?: Adam picks a team of popular athletes over his friends in gym class. Erica decides that she wants to leave home to go to college. (S3 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Rush: When Barry insists that Beverly always favours Adam, she tries to make amends. Murray's not happy about Erica's new boyfriend, a fanatical music fan. (S3 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Ringmaster Keifth: Cam tries to make up for his Thanksgiving debacle by hosting a New Year feast. And Phil's not sure how to feel about his dad dating his childhood babysitter. (S8 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sarge & Pea: Cam is incensed when a rude parent robs him of a precious Lily moment during her dance recital. Jay, Claire and Mitch unexpectedly run into Dede at a family wedding. (S8 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Spin a Yarn: Gordon tries to save the struggling Spin a Yarn restaurant in California. Despite an expensive refurbishment, the business is tearing apart its owners' marriage. (S5 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Charlie's: Gordon Ramsay visits Italian bistro Charlie's, where the pasta's soggy, the lasagne's a liability and the chef can't even cook a meatball. (S5 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Mole: When an Internal Affairs investigator reveals that there's a mole in the precinct, Peralta and Holt must find out who it is before Wuntch catches on. (S2 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Jake and Sophia: Peralta hits it off with a woman in a bar, only to find out that she's the defence attorney representing a suspect who he wants to put in jail. (S2 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The President Wore Pearls: Principal Skinner cancels sport, art and music at the school to save cash, so the students - and the police - go on strike. With Michael Moore. (S15 Ep3/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Regina Monologues: The Simpsons go to London with $1000 that Bart found, but Homer crashes the hire car into the Queen and gets locked in the Tower. Tony Blair guest stars. (S15 Ep4/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Recipe for Death II: Kiss the Cook: Adam asks Murray for money to film his own action movie, while Erica and Beverly go shopping for clothes. (S4 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Ho-ly K.I.T.T.: A shared love of the TV show Knight Rider brings Murray and his brother Marvin together. Beverly invites Lainey and Bill to Thanksgiving dinner. (S4 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: All Things Being Equal: Gloria, Claire, Haley, Alex, Lily, Luke and Manny each have very different ways of supporting gender equality. (S8 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Alone Time: Everyone deserves a little alone time, but when Mitch and Jay separately seek out a much-needed retreat from the family, they end up at the same resort. (S8 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Windbreaker City: The team are assigned the role of hostages at a Homeland Security counter-terrorism training exercise. (S2 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Wednesday Incident: When Peralta notices that Captain Holt is in a bad mood, he teams up with Holt's husband Kevin to find out what's gone wrong. (S2 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Smart and Smarter: Lisa searches for a new identity when she worries that her position as the clever Simpson is under threat from Maggie. (S15 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Ziff Who Came to Dinner: The Simpsons find Marge's high school prom date Artie Ziff squatting in their loft, and he's planning to frame Homer... (S15 Ep14/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - Homer and Her Sisters: A self-help expert prompts Homer to do something unthinkable: get to know Patty and Selma. (S36 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: American History X-cellent: When Mr Burns is arrested for art fraud, Smithers shakes things up at the power plant, so Homer and his friends plot to break Mr Burns out of jail. (S21 Ep17/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: BFFs Emma and Dani have disastrous dating records - will double dating help? Aire from Venezuela wants someone 'a bit crazy'. Does colourful-trouser-wearing Mark fit the bill? (S22 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers cast their eyes over It's A Sin, Ant & Dec's Saturday Night Takeaway, Surviving Death, This Morning, and BBC News on Boris Johnson's Covid road map announcement. (S17 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: On the box this time: The Late Late Show with James Corden, Married at First Sight Australia, Drawers Off, Your Honor, Million Pound Pawn, Pooch Perfect, and Stand Up & Deliver. (S17 Ep2)

Film4.uk.title: Polite Society
Film4.uk.description: (2023) Nida Manzoor's kick-ass martial-arts anti-romcom stars Priya Kansara as a college student and wannabe stuntwoman who wants to save her older sister from an undesirable marriage.

Film4.uk.title: Fighting with My Family
Film4.uk.description: (2019) Stephen Merchant's heart-warming comedy-drama based on the life of British WWE wrestler Paige. With Nick Frost, Dwayne Johnson, Lena Headey and Florence Pugh.

Film4.uk.title: xXx
Film4.uk.description: (2002) Action thriller starring Vin Diesel as Xander Cage: a thrill-seeking extreme sports enthusiast, stuntman and rebellious athlete-turned-reluctant spy. With Samuel L Jackson.

Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: This Gun for Hire
Film4.uk.description: (1942) Classic noir starring Alan Ladd and Veronica Lake. As a cold-blooded assassin seek vengeance for a double cross, he unwisely falls for the girlfriend of the cop who's pursuing him.

Film4.uk.title: Roman Holiday
Film4.uk.description: (1953) Audrey Hepburn won her only Oscar in this romance as a bored princess who runs away from her duties and meets an American journalist (Gregory Peck), who shows her Rome.

Film4.uk.title: The Sheriff of Fractured Jaw
Film4.uk.description: (1959) Comedy western with Kenneth More. An English gunsmith decides the Wild West is the best market for his wares, but little does he expect to end up sheriff of a lawless frontier town.

Film4.uk.title: Man in the Saddle
Film4.uk.description: (1951) Western. Randolph Scott stars as a rancher who's the target of unwelcome harassment by his richer and more powerful neighbour. With Alexander Knox, Joan Leslie and Ellen Drew.

Film4.uk.title: Flight of the Phoenix
Film4.uk.description: (2004) Drama. Dennis Quaid stars as the captain of an aircraft downed in the desert. There's no hope of rescue, unless he and the survivors can build another plane from the wreckage.

Film4.uk.title: Knock at the Cabin
Film4.uk.description: (2023) M Night Shyamalan's jarringly intimate end-of-days horror with Dave Bautista. An armed group insist that a family of three must make an impossible life-or-death choice.

Film4.uk.title: Glass
Film4.uk.description: (2019) M. Night Shyamalan directs an all-star cast in this genre-bending superhero sequel. Three superhumans team up to escape a psychiatric ward. With Bruce Willis in a cagoule.

Film4.uk.title: Terminator Genisys
Film4.uk.description: (2015) Sci-fi thriller with Arnold Schwarzenegger and Emilia Clarke. Part five of the franchise follows Sarah Connor in an alternate timeline to the previous movies, as she takes on Skynet.

Film4.uk.title: The Desert Fox
Film4.uk.description: (1951) Drama. James Mason stars in Henry Hathaway's sympathetic portrait of Field Marshal Erwin Rommel in the final years of his life during the Second World War. With Jessica Tandy.

Film4.uk.title: River of No Return
Film4.uk.description: (1954) Western with Robert Mitchum and Marilyn Monroe. An ex-con and a saloon singer steer a raft through hostile territory to face a showdown with her crooked fiancé. With Rory Calhoun.

Film4.uk.title: Dad's Army
Film4.uk.description: (1971) Film version of the popular comedy series set in 1940. The Walmington-on-Sea Home Guard, led by Arthur Lowe's Captain Mainwaring, bumble through a series of misadventures.

Film4.uk.title: Le Mans '66
Film4.uk.description: (2019) Oscar-winning sports drama starring Matt Damon and Christian Bale. In the 60s, Ford set out to build a car that can defeat Ferrari at the 24 Hours of Le Mans race.

Film4.uk.title: Daredevil
Film4.uk.description: (2003) Superhero fantasy. Ben Affleck is a blind lawyer who turns vigilante by night. Jennifer Garner plays his lover and Colin Farrell the villain who endangers them both. Strong violence.

Film4.uk.title: The Last Duel
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Historical drama from director Ridley Scott. Trial by combat is the only option to save a noblewoman's honour. With Jodie Comer, Matt Damon, Adam Driver and Ben Affleck.

Film4.uk.title: Wildfire
Film4.uk.description: (2020) Tense drama set near Northern Ireland's border. When two sisters are reunited after one had disappeared, their lives become increasingly complicated as old wounds start to open.
